##DESCRIPTION
##  Algebra problem: true or false for inequality 
##ENDDESCRIPTION


## DBsubject(Calculus - single variable)
## DBchapter(Infinite sequences and series)
## DBsection(Fourier series)
## Date(7/18/2011)
## Institution(Alfred University)
